@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-primary">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="lead">At Parking Zone, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect the following information to provide and improve our services:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you register, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you provide voluntarily.</li>
        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> To provide parking services, we may collect location data when you use our app or website.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We collect payment details when you make a reservation.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We collect information about how you use the Parking Zone website, including access logs, device information, and browser types.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Manage your parking reservations.</li>
        <li>Provide location-based parking options.</li>
        <li>Process payments securely.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you regarding your account and reservations.</li>
        <li>Analyze site usage to improve our services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. How We Share Your Information</h3>
    <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except in the following cases:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We share your data with trusted partners who help us operate our services (e.g., payment processors, hosting providers).</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law or in response to valid requests by government authorities.</li>
        <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger or acquisition, your information may be transferred to the new entity.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to track the activity on our website and store certain information. You can control your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

    <h3>5. Data Security</h3>
    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h3>6. Your Data Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your data.</li>
        <li>Request corrections to any inaccurate information.</li>
        <li>Delete your data (subject to legal requirements).</li>
        <li>Object to or restrict how we use your data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <h3>8. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@parkingzone.com</p>
    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +123-456-7890</p>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script>
        // Add any necessary JavaScript for this page
    </script>
}
